'''Oussama Benbot''' ({{langx|ar|أُسَامَة بن بُوط}}; born 11 October 1994) is an Algerian professional [[association football|footballer]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.matchendirect.fr/joueur/oussama-benbot.html|title=Oussama Benbot}}</ref> who plays as a [[goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for [[USM Alger]] in the [[Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1]] and the [[Algeria national football team|Algeria national team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elmoudjahid.dz/fr/sports/usma-oussama-benbot-signe-pour-deux-ans-13279|title=USMA : Oussama Benbot signe pour deux ans|access-date=20 August 2021|archive-date=20 August 2021|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210820155002/http://www.elmoudjahid.dz/fr/sports/usma-oussama-benbot-signe-pour-deux-ans-13279|url-status=dead}}</ref>

==Club career==
In 2018, Benbot signed a contract with [[JS Kabylie]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dzfoot.com/2018/06/10/jsk-oussama-benbot-deuxieme-gardien-129137.php|title=JSK : Oussama Benbot deuxième gardien |website=dzfoot.com |date=10 June 2018 |access-date=10 June 2018}}</ref> 
On 14 August 2021, he joined [[USM Alger]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://africasport.dz/2021/08/14/jsk-benbot-signe-a-lusma/|title=JSK/Benbot Signe À L’USMA |website=africasport.dz |date=14 August 2021 |access-date=14 August 2021}}</ref> On 16 August 2023, he extended his contract until 2026.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.lescore.dz/2023/08/usm-alger-belaid-benbot-et-alilet-prolonges/ |title=USM Alger: dix cadres prolongés d'un seul coup |website=lescore.dz |date=16 August 2023 |access-date=16 August 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://rivalite.dz/football-usma-dix-joueurs-prolonges-dun-coup/ |title=Football: USMA: Dix joueurs prolongés d'un coup |website=rivalite.dz |date=17 August 2023 |access-date=17 August 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://mediafootdz.dz/usm-alger-huit-joueurs-rempilent-jusquen-2026/ |title=USM Alger : Huit joueurs rempilent jusqu'en 2026 |website=mediafootdz.dz |date=17 August 2023 |access-date=17 August 2023}}</ref>

==International career==
On 30 May 2023, the [[Algerian Football Federation|FAF]] publish the list of [[Djamel Belmadi]] for the two matches of the month of June, Where is called Oussama Benbot for the first time.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.dzfoot.com/equipes-nationales/en-la-liste-de-belmadi-contre-louganda-et-la-tunisie-242811.html |title=EN : La liste de Belmadi contre l'Ouganda et la Tunisie |website=dzfoot.com |date=30 May 2023 |access-date=21 June 2023}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://lagazettedufennec.com/belaid-si-pas-maintenant-cest-quand/ |title=Zineddine Belaïd, si pas maintenant c’est quand ? |website=Lagazette du fennec |date=7 October 2023 |access-date=31 December 2023}}</ref> On 29 December 2023, Benbot was named by [[Djamel Belmadi]] to Algeria's 26-man squad for the [[2023 Africa Cup of Nations]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.dzfoot.com/equipes-nationales/officiel-la-liste-des-verts-pour-la-can-est-parue-252031.html |title=Officiel : La liste des Verts pour la CAN est parue ! |website=DZfoot |date=29 December 2023 |access-date=30 December 2023}}</ref>

